For those commenting about SASS having this forever etc, note that this goes a step further:<p><pre><code>    :root { --color: blue; }
    div { --color: green; }
    #alert { --color: red; }
    * { color: var(--color); }
</code></pre>
You can&#x27;t accomplish that with SASS today. More info [0].<p>In fact, this feature isn&#x27;t even covered with cssnext:<p><pre><code>    The current transformation for custom properties aims to provide a future-proof way of using a limited subset (to top-level :root selector) ... [1]
</code></pre>
